<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thangvan khuo lunlaia ngabang lengsa,
 Simlei gitloh zanbang thimah a hung;
 Van mipi simsen lohte'n gihawih tawh,
 Hung tha'n Bethlehem dai la'n a awi ui.

[V2]
 Nunnawpna chung sunni Bethlehem tang chungah
 A hung suok ie mitin-a dingin;
 Sietlei thangvan mi chengin Amah chawian ding,
 A chawihatna zaila lawptakin saitiu.

[V3]
 2. Suohlam miching leh Belampute chu,
 Chamna Lal hung pieng lawmin a hung ui;
 Ka lautha nang le hawlin Hukdampa,
 Na gitloh ziekin albang A vai hi

[V4]
 3. Kanaan gam sunni tum ding ka thilin,
 A kuol gankuong sungah maw,Hukdampa;
 Amah lawm dingin kuomah a hung puou,
 Chieh hitiu aw, Amah chawian dingin.</lyrics>
<title>Chamna Lal</title>
<hymn_number>14</hymn_number>
</song>